Cursor movement            Delete
---------------            ------
      ¼ ½ Character        CTRL ¼ ½       Character
SHIFT ¼ ½ Word             CTRL SHIFT ¼ ½ Word
ALT   ¼ ½ Start/End line   CTRL ALT ¼     Line
      ¾ ¿ Line             CTRL ALT ½  to End of line
SHIFT ¾ ¿ Page
ALT   ¾ ¿ Scroll
CTRL  ¾ ¿ Search backward/forward

Single-key commands
-------------------
TAB      Tabulate
ESC      Undo changes on current line
F1       Help
F2       Re-execute last command line
F3       Enter command line
SHIFT F3 Edit last command line
F4       Change Insert/Overwrite mode
F5       Redraw screen

Extended commands
-----------------
A/s/    Insert line <s> after current line
B       Move to bottom of file
BE      Mark block end
BF/s/   Backwards find string <s>
BS      Mark block start
CE      Cursor to end of line
CL      Cursor one position left
CR      Cursor one position right
CS      Cursor to start of line
D       Delete current line
DB      Delete block
DC      Delete character under cursor
DW      Delete word right from cursor
E/s/t/  Exchange <s> into <t>
EQ/s/t/ Exchange but query first
F/s/    Find string <s>
I/s/    Insert line <s> before current
IB      Insert copy of block
IF/s/   Insert file <s>
J       Join current line with next
M n     Move to line <n>
N       Move to next line
NW      Move to next word
P       Move to previous line
PW      Move to previous word
Q       Quit editor without saving text
R/s/    Re-enter editor with file <s>
RP      Repeat until error
RT      Return to last line (max. 3x)
S       Split line at cursor
SA/s/   Save text to file <s> (or default file)
SB      Show block
SH      Show current editor status
SL n    Set left margin at <n>
SR n    Set right margin at <n>
ST n    Set tab distance to <n>
T       Move to top of file
TY/s/   Type string <s>
U       Undo changes on current line
WB/s/   Write block to file <s>
X       Exit, writing text back
